Bootstrap
-------------
Bootstrap latest version is 5.x.

Bootstrap is the most popular and powerful front-end (Html,CSS,Javascript) framework for faster and easier responsive web development.

Bootstrap gives us the ability to create a flexible and responsive web layouts with much less efforts.

Bootstrap was originally designed by Twitter.


Advantages
--------------------
It is very easy to use.
It saves a lot of time.
Anyone who is having basic knowledge of Html and css can use bootstrap.
It is used to create responsive websites.

A website is called responsive website, which can automatically adjust itself to look good on all the devices from smartphone to desktops.

we can create with bootstrap like
--------------------------------------------
we can create responsive websites
we can create different types of form layouts
we can create different types of navigation bars
we can create different types of modals.
we can create different types of tooltips
we can create image slider
we can create alert boxes.



to download bootstrap go to the official website
getbootstrap.com


